  "description": "Torus topology with a slow, deep modulation that creates tidal swell — the reverb level rises and falls on a long cycle. Feedback is near-threshold, so the swell amplifies instead of dampening. At the peak of each cycle the spatial wash floods the mix; at the trough it retreats. Dangerous and beautiful.",
